        "Description": "Lucy Phillips has a grotesque outfit, an outfit so garish that it will burn into your retinas... Also with some hint of racism.  Seriously? A sky and cloud design on &quot;MC Hammer&quot; pants with a stupid ankle elastic? Our benefactor, the decade of the 1980&apos;s, you know the decade that had mustard sashes and ketchup boots!? It  implores you to do the right thing and elimate this abombination.  Style is a personal thing... unless it offends everyone single human around you.  It&apos;s an affront on taste...",
